OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly showery rain and
OL,6,Fthunderstorms soon clearing eastwards.
OL,7,FBecoming fine with further sunshine
OL,8,Ffor a time, still very hot, but
OL,9,Fmarkedly less so than Friday. Further
OL,10,Fshowers and thunderstorms possible
OL,11,Flater.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAn unsettled evening with
OL,14,Fshowers and thunderstorms likely.
OL,15,FTurning more settled overnight and
OL,16,Fsome breaks in the cloud develop.
OL,17,FTemperatures remaining warm overnight
OL,18,Fwith light southwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
