OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FFresher conditions spreading
OL,6,Fto all parts into Sunday. Cloudy at
OL,7,Ftimes with some sunny intervals during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. More seasonable
OL,9,Ftemperatures than expected. Winds
OL,10,Fmoderate southwesterly, breezy along
OL,11,Fthe coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,14,Fis looking dry and settled, Turning
OL,15,Fmore unsettled on Tuesday with
OL,16,Fsunshine and showers. Wednesday starts
OL,17,Fof sunny, then clouds over later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
